name: Future Art Access All Art Pass VeeFriends edition

metadata.description:
**ACCESS ALL ART PASS**

All ‘Access All Art Pass’ holders can claim 4 x exclusive Future Art Curated NFT drops.

These will include limited edition runs of artworks and new NFT

Projects from some of the world’s most exciting crypto artists.

**ACCESS ALL ART PASS EVENTS**

‘Access All Art Pass’ gives you VIP access to All Future Art events across the globe including confirmed shows in Ibiza, Sydney, London and New York in 2022

**VIP COLLECTOR & CURATOR SESSIONS**

Grab a drink and take a private walk through a preview of each show with Future Art curators Sats Moon and Dave Goode and meet some of our featured artists face to face.

Artwork by Burst_ Music by Future Art

[futureart.io](https://futureart.io)
